    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The more widely spaced lines visible in the texture of laid paper, made by the wire mesh at the bottom of the tray in which it is made. Laid lines are the fine lines running through the chain lines.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
